        <p>We use the equivalent of <xref rid="E19" ref-type="disp-formula">Equation (19)</xref> with <inline-formula id="IE78"><mml:math id="IM78" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold-italic">Ï</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mrow><mml:msub><mml:mrow><mml:mo>Ï</mml:mo></mml:mrow><mml:mi>o</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:mrow></mml:mrow></mml:math></inline-formula> to evaluate these expectations and iterate until the value of <italic toggle="yes">Ï</italic> converges.</p>
